---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Room of Projected Horizons — Michalina Sablik">
  <div class="container page-content">
    <h1>Room of Projected Horizons</h1>
    <p class="exhibition-detail-venue">Galeria Promocyjna | 2022</p>
    <div class="exhibition-detail-body">
      <p>Inaugural institutional solo exhibition featuring a video installation created collaboratively with members of the Kiki House of Sarmata. Examines ballroom culture through an intimate lens, presenting participants stripped of makeup and costumes in black-and-white format. "Bo&#380;na tells her own story through conversations and intimate questions asked of the members of a queer family." Recurring themes: embodiment, desire, ability, solitude, transformation, and self-love. Explores how gender operates as performance through repeated gestures and behavioral patterns, drawing on Judith Butler's theoretical framework. "Heralds the beginning of a new era: the crisis of cultural gender and the arrival of new, fluid identities."</p>
    </div>
    <div class="exhibition-detail-credits">
      <p><strong>Artist:</strong> Bo&#380;na Wydrowska</p>
      <p><strong>Curators:</strong> Michalina Sablik, Kaja Werbanowska</p>
    </div>
    <div class="exhibition-gallery" style="margin-top: 2.5rem; display: grid; gap: 1rem;">
      <img src="/images/exhibitions/room-of-projected-horizons/1.jpg" alt="Exhibition view" loading="lazy" style="width:100%; border-radius: 4px;" />
      <img src="/images/exhibitions/room-of-projected-horizons/2.jpg" alt="Exhibition view" loading="lazy" style="width:100%; border-radius: 4px;" />
      <img src="/images/exhibitions/room-of-projected-horizons/3.jpg" alt="Exhibition view" loading="lazy" style="width:100%; border-radius: 4px;" />
      <img src="/images/exhibitions/room-of-projected-horizons/4.jpg" alt="Exhibition view" loading="lazy" style="width:100%; border-radius: 4px;" />
      <img src="/images/exhibitions/room-of-projected-horizons/5.jpg" alt="Exhibition view" loading="lazy" style="width:100%; border-radius: 4px;" />
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
